Ascension.MOD			DESC:Mythic: If you expend one use of mythic power when casting this spell, the duration increases to 1 day per level, and you can use yourself as the focus for this spell instead of a lesser artifact. If you're the focus, the targets retain their mythic tier only while they're within 100 feet of you, and if you die, the spell immediately ends and all targets gain 1d4 permanent negative levels.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Mythic Spell,Ascension
Deathless.MOD			DESC:Mythic: If you expend one use of mythic power when you cast the spell, you become an anchor for the souls of you and your cohorts. The range increases to 30 feet, and instead of affecting one creature, it affects all allies within a 30-foot radius emanation centered on you. Augmented (8th): If you expend three uses of mythic power, the range increases to 1 mile, and the area to a 1-mile radius emanation centered on you.|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Mythic Spell,Deathless
